2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |     3     |     4      |    5    |
| Hobby   | chess | video-games | gardening | hiking | sudoku |

