.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, thriller, superhero, musical
1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7
4. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |      4      |  5  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | thriller | satire | time-travel | musical |

