1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching zombie movies##7
3. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching western movies##7
4. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |   3    |      4       |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | zombie | fantasy | animation | western |

